title: Ranked 5v5 team
body:
Hello! Looking for a Gold ranked 5v5 team to play on! I am active and Gold V at the moment. Feel free to check my ranked stats. If anyone is recruiting that is in Gold. Please let me know! Thanks. Hit me up with an add and msg me please.
IGN: Xiaoma
P.S. I main Top and ADC. Can do all roles but my weakest role is jungle.
